                    <span>If there was any doubt before, this book proves that the multi-talented Jim Bouton really can write. He is also a terrific researcher, reporter, entrepreneur, & tilter-of-windmills. This book is about a lot more than baseball, but it is clearly a CASEY Award calibre book nevertheless.</span>
                  
              
